{"type": "article", "id": 22687, "title": "一种复合木板，竟可以支撑起一个办公室的设计", "description": "智利的林业公司开发了可弯曲的木板，它能成为大有前途的材料吗？", "date": "2016-02-23T07:00:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23792, "name": "木板"}, {"id": 501, "name": "办公室"}, {"id": 23793, "name": "Arauco"}, {"id": 23794, "name": "The Andes House"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 142, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608123840rFJNhPC5YZ9WbvHu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.arauco.cl/default.asp\">ARAUCO</a> 是智利一家林业产品公司，已有将近 50 年历史。依托南美一带 160 多万公顷的森林资源成为全球排名前三的纸浆制造商、木材生产商和板材生产商。中国是它最重要的市场，2009 年的销售额占到 45%（美洲只占到 8%）。它也同时是中国主要的纸浆供应商。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>ARAUCO近期推出一种复合木板 <a href=\"http://www.arauco.cl/\">cholguan</a> 板，利用湿法制作，液态混合物在高温下干燥形成单面光滑的硬质纤维薄板，密度比普通中密度纤维板高 35%。既具有柔韧性，也能耐湿。他们邀请智利设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.theandeshouse.com/TAH/\">The Andes House</a> 测验并开发这种材料，使它满足现代人生活和工作的需求。</p>\n<p>The Andes House 花了 6 个月完成开发，他们设计了 5 种不同的模板。在两层材料的中间使用木条做支撑，可以相互搭配安装，具有灵活、轻盈和低价的特征。</p>\n<p>最终完成的办公隔断展示了他们的开发。模块化的物件可以搭配配件，就像一扇扇屏风。在隔断上还可以挂着用 cholguan 制作的文件夹等小文具。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123830GCpTMacWExK5Xfzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123831t7AI0nl5a8sKxbCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123831lSNO6eXHzpEVW7gq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123832UKXfVsvmBjqwO2E5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123832FHgsCASxNPpI0l1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081238337d1IQOshzTH9WEer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123833UY1x50P8csMAWL6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123834hIHdxGKBCgk53eOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">还有一组桌面上的设计，可以作为文具类型的隔板、文件夹使用。经过搭配后，竟可以支撑起一个办公室的设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123834fsLxnvUgN4KE23Ij.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123835WzFeV6Lp3h9gURZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081238353nUBFM5t4Clxu1e9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081238351ozTx7bhtB6WvPdO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123836783XEkVvsu1ditmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123836AZo3SRqiEVNKyp1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123837atDeEIzj6xWYJ95y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123837Io6Fhw5tEX8B7juN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123838e6C3BtNR7uLUFWQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123838A91EoC8OhGcjNSik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608123839OLpWteNG7PwV69na.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/781826/the-andes-houses-ensamble-project-uses-hardboard-to-create-workspaces\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/the-andes-house-proyecto-ensamble-01-29-2016/\">designboom</a></p>\n\n\n"}